<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><kml xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/kml/2.2" xmlns:kml="http://www.opengis.net/kml/2.2" xmlns:TEI="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><Document><Placemark><address><![CDATA[Bergama]]></address><name><![CDATA[Bergama]]></name><description><![CDATA[<h1>Description of "<a href="http://www.getty.edu/vow/TGNFullDisplay?find=&amp;place=&amp;nation=&amp;english=Y&amp;subjectid=7016140">Bergama</a>"</h1>Under Persian rule 5th cen. BC; prosperous Hellenistic city during rule of Eumenes I &amp; Attalids (282-133 BC); bequeathed by Attalus III to Rome 133 BC; to Byzantines after fall of Rome; passed to Ottomans 14th cen.; ruins a "text" of Hellenistic art.<p>Description from <a href="http://www.getty.edu/">Getty Thesaurus</a></p>]]></description><Point><coordinates>27.1667,39.1333</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Document></kml>